{
  "stem": "1581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this is one of the horrible nightmares and unforgettable experiences when you saw your beloved mother, deprived of my support and help, put into a transport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the last I saw was when one of these SS animals pushed her into one of these wagons which were only for, for cattle and not for people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was the last I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Needless to say, we always were hoping against hope to somehow see them again alive, and we were talking of nothing else but the time when we will be again reunited with our mothers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What prompted our optimism, again, we followed very closely what was going on in the world and by now, Hitler didn't do very well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Stalin has occurred, and--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- There was-- there were not only SS people or Gestapo people controlling us, but there was a whole group of Czech gendarmes who were very benevolent and obviously trying to help us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In addition, they knew that I was a doctor, and I had a good reputation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them had a tonsil abscess, which is a very painful infection in the throat, and I treated him and operated on him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since then, he-- he really helped us as much as he could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought us all the news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were informed what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew-- as a matter of fact, we knew much more than what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jewish word for fairy tales which are wishful thinking is called a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was-- jokefully we had an agency called the [NON-ENGLISH] agency.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
